# Una variable categórica una continua

## Una variable categórica una continua

* geom_boxplot
* geom_jitter
* geom_violin
* geom_bar

## geom_jitter


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(iris, aes(x = Species, y = Sepal.Width)) + geom_jitter(aes(color = Species))
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Clase4Visualizacion_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-12-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


## geom_violin


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(iris, aes(x = Species, y = Sepal.Width)) + geom_violin(fill = "red")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Clase4Visualizacion_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-13-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


## Se pueden combinar


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(iris, aes(x = Species, y = Sepal.Width)) + geom_violin() +
    geom_jitter(aes(color = Species))
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Clase4Visualizacion_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-14-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


## Pero el orden importa


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(iris, aes(x = Species, y = Sepal.Width)) + geom_jitter(aes(color = Species)) +
    geom_violin()
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Clase4Visualizacion_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-15-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


# Como reordenar las variables

## fct_reorder (Reordenar por otra variable)



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(iris, aes(x = fct_reorder(Species, Sepal.Width),
    y = Sepal.Width)) + geom_boxplot(aes(fill = Species),
    notch = T) + theme_bw()
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Clase4Visualizacion_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-16-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


## fct_reorder (cont)



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(iris, aes(x = fct_reorder(Species, Sepal.Width),
    y = Sepal.Width)) + geom_boxplot(aes(fill = Species),
    notch = T) + theme_bw() + xlab("lo que se me ocurra")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Clase4Visualizacion_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-17-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


## fct_relevel


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(iris, aes(x = fct_relevel(Species, "setosa",
    "virginica"), y = Sepal.Width)) + geom_boxplot(aes(fill = Species),
    notch = T) + theme_bw() + xlab("lo que se me ocurra")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Clase4Visualizacion_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-18-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


